channel.title: Your opinions?
channel.description:
So after I finish Vicious Revolution v2 and its out of Alpha and Beta, I was thinking about starting a small side project to remember us of the good old days even before Allstar. My first RSPS was named New Start on suba-studios.com. Videos of it below, and it was spawn, pk, but you had to click certain objects to train your levels. Dummies for Attack, Strength, and Defence, Haybales for magic, targets for range etc. The max Combat level was like 180 something, max for each level was 120 I believe and it took a few days if not more of clicking a tree to get that. My question is if any of you would be interested in playing it? It just brings back my good memories. :P

item.title: Your opinions?
item.dc:creator: @Uncalled Uncalled
item.description:
@Uncalled wrote:

I remember a server, oddly similar to the one shown, named Aarscape. I think the highest combat level was 252 and the highest achievable level was 185. Black full helm, dragon chainbody, Torag’s hammers, rune platelegs, dragon boots, amulet of fury, and berserker ring made it to where you were able to one-hit anyone fairly easily. If you didn’t one-hit your opponent, almost guaranteed he would you. It wasn’t spawn, but everything was extremely easy to get as well as all leveling.
